    		Citibank
    		<p>My most recent job was as a collections specialist for Citibank. I would make outbound calls to people that were behind on their credit card payments and use negotioation tactics to resolve the accounts. In order to succeed we had to hit strict goals. When we fell behind we had a coach there to give us constructive criticism. Working here gave me the ability to focus on whats important and be persistant.
    		</p>
    	</div>
