    		<p>My time at Dish Network started out with me being entry level technical support. I was able to promote twice into the position of broadband specialist. Each department I worked in taught me to think logicaly and give precise directions to customers. Now instead of trying random ways to fix something I take a structured approach for quick and efficient resolutions.
    		</p>
