    		<p>Afni was my first call center job. At Afni, I worked their Verizon Wireless customer service contract. This is the job that majorly influenced my desicion to become a developer. Hearing customer frusteration with the company website and even my own with the company intranet made me want to be one of the people to make them better.
    		</p>
    	</div>
